sequenceDiagram
    participant Nginx as Nginx / DVWA<br/>(dvwa_access.log)
    participant Watcher as Log Watcher<br/>(tail -f)
    participant Engine as Rule Engine<br/>+ Classifier
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant WS as WebSocket Server<br/>(FastAPI)
    participant Dash as Dashboard<br/>(React)

    Note over Dash,WS: 1. Saat dashboard dibuka, koneksi WebSocket<br/>langsung dibuka & TETAP TERBUKA
    Dash->>WS: connect (ws://server/ws/alerts)
    WS-->>Dash: connected (saluran siap)

    Note over Nginx,Engine: 2. Serangan terjadi & tercatat di log
    Nginx->>Watcher: baris log baru masuk
    Watcher->>Engine: parse + preprocess (URL decode, normalisasi)
    Engine->>Engine: rule matching regex<br/>(XSS / SQLi / Multiple?)

    alt Terdeteksi serangan
        Engine->>DB: simpan hasil deteksi
        Engine->>WS: kirim data alert ke server
        Note over WS,Dash: 3. Server PUSH alert lewat saluran<br/>yang sudah terbuka (tanpa diminta)
        WS-->>Dash: push alert realtime
        Dash->>Dash: tampilkan alert DETIK ITU JUGA<br/>(tanpa refresh)
    else Normal
        Engine->>DB: simpan sebagai Normal
        Note over Engine,Dash: tidak ada alert dikirim
    end
